\mathtt{f}:\mathbb{Z}\rightarrow \mathbb{R}
\mathtt{f}[n]=\int_{n-\frac{1}{2}}^{n+\frac{1}{2}} f(x)\ dx
\mathtt{f}[n]=\text{rect}(x)\ast \ (\ \text{comb}(x)\cdot(\text{rect}(x)\star f(x))\ ) \text{  evaluated at }n
