(comb \ast rect)(x) = 1,
(f\ast rect(\cdot-n))(x) =\int_{n-1/2}^{n+1/2}f(x-y)dy, 
\int_{\Bbb R}dx  \int_{n-1/2}^{n+1/2}f(x-y)dy = \int_{\Bbb R}f(x)dx.
